#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Field names are case-insensitive. Supported formats: mp4, mkv, avi, mov, "
"webm and others supported by MediaInfo (pymediainfo). When combined with "
"<code>{im:…}</code> or <code>{au:…}</code>, non-matching fields are "
"silently empty. With only <code>{vi:…}</code> fields, a default is "
"recommended."
msgstr ""
"Les noms de champs sont insensibles à la casse. Formats pris en charge : "
